{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-044__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-001", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-044", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-044__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "chapter", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "老子 44", "sort_key": "044.000", "text_original": "名與身孰親？\n\n身與貨孰多？\n\n得與亡孰病？\n\n是故甚愛必大費，多藏必厚亡，\n\n知足不辱，知止不殆，可以長久。", "text_normalized": "名與身孰親？\n\n身與貨孰多？\n\n得與亡孰病？\n\n是故甚愛必大費，多藏必厚亡，\n\n知足不辱，知止不殆，可以長久。", "notes": ""}
